metadata.description: Complete 256 Odu system with authentic naming and patterns

major_odu.name: Eji Ogbe
major_odu.pattern: I I I I I I I I
major_odu.guidance: Embrace the full power of Eji Ogbe. Light, clarity, divine wisdom guides your path.
major_odu.spiritual_significance: Primary Eji Ogbe - Light, clarity, divine wisdom
major_odu.traditional_story: In ancient times, when Eji Ogbe was cast, the elders would speak of light, clarity, divine wisdom. This Odu teaches us about spiritual growth and divine wisdom.
major_odu.modern_application: Apply Eji Ogbe wisdom in contemporary life by focusing on light, clarity, divine wisdom while maintaining spiritual awareness.
